                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The cythnophorian uses Fungal Possession</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> All creatures in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] must attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:26] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure. Affected creatures are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] for as long as they're sickened. Once a creature attempts this save, it's temporarily immune for 1 minute.</p>"
