                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:22]</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 round</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Damage[2d6[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Damage[4d6[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Damage[6d6[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Confused] (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @Damage[6d6[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Controlled] (1 round). A creature that dies while infected with creeping death immediately releases a burst of spores as if using the cythnophorian's Spore Cloud ability. If the corpse is not burned, it rises as the host of a new cythnophorian 12 hours later.</p>"
